                    <span>Gr8 book if you need assistance with xml programming and also helps in using all methods of reading, writing and using xml. Dino! High five.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Dino is the man</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
